## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Voice Selection:** The plan uses "Adam" (authoritative male). Would you prefer a different ElevenLabs voice for a more formal/news-anchor tone?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Image Strategy Priority:** Should we prioritize Tavily-fetched real photos, or generate all 8 backgrounds with the AI image tool for visual consistency? The plan currently tries Tavily first with AI fallback.

