## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Run `npx tsx scripts/fetch-images-apr14.ts` вҖ” verify 8 images downloaded
2. Run `npx tsx scripts/generate-voiceover-apr14.ts` вҖ” verify 8 MP3 files generated
3. Run `npm run dev` вҖ” open Remotion Studio, verify `trump-iran-apr14` composition loads
4. Preview composition вҖ” verify all 8 scenes render with images, captions, and audio

### Manual Verification
- Confirm word-by-word caption animation is smooth and readable
- Verify formal tone matches documentary style (no hype)
- Check 1-minute total duration
- Validate image positioning (full-bleed, no stretching, proper Ken Burns)
